# Project Manager Server

## 🎯 Available Tools

This project has access to Project Manager server tools for enhanced project management and AI assistance.

### 📋 Goals Management

- `goals_list()` - List active project goals
- `goals_add({title: "Goal Title"})` - Add new goal
- `goals_update({id: 1, status: "done"})` - Update goal status

### 📝 Cursor Rules Management

- `cursor_rules_list()` - List active cursor rules
- `cursor_rules_add({name: "Rule Name", category: "general", content: "Rule content"})` - Add new rule
- `cursor_rules_update({id: 1, content: "Updated content"})` - Update existing rule
- `cursor_rules_delete({id: 1})` - Delete rule
- `cursor_rules_suggest({category: "general"})` - Suggest community rules
- `cursor_rules_install({rule_name: "rule-name"})` - Install rule from community

